Type: Package
Title: Insert source code into documentation using the @code tag with roxygen2
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jacob Scott
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: Use the @code tag in roxygen2 documentation to insert the code
    for the function in question, with comments and whitespace in tact. 
